AG for Air Greenland A/S. P.O. Box 150, 3900 Nuuk
Tlf. + 299 38 39 59
Suluk is produced for Air Greenland Inc.
by Sermitsiaq.
AG, P.O. Box 150, 3900 Nuuk.
